        <div><a class="project-link" href="/" target="_blank"><h4>mattopie.com</h4></a><a class="git-link" href="https://www.github.com/matthew-opie/blazor-portfolio-wasm/" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i>Github</a></div>
